LucidSim and Benchmark Suite
============================

Experiments
-----------

**1. To generate data**

-  run `weaver.render_node <weaver/render_node.py>`__ in the
   dream-weaver repository
-  run teacher streamer, turn off streaming
-  run vuer_monitor to monitor the images

**2. To Behavior Clone**

.. code-block:: shell

   lucidim.learning --env <env> --algo <algo> --num_timesteps <num_timesteps> --log_path <log_path> --save_path <save_path>

**To Evaluate**

-  run
   `lucidsim_experiments.sweeps.evaluation_sweep <lucidsim_experiments/sweeps/evaluation_sweep.py>`__
   to generate the sweeps
-  run
   `lucidsim_experiments.launch_evaluation.py <lucidsim_experiments/launch_evaluation.py>`__
   to launch the evaluation runs

Environments
------------

LucidSim Environments: each with ``lucidsim``, ``rgb``, ``heightmap``,
``depth`` render.

-  ☐ Parkour (+ cones)
-  ☐ Stairs (+ cones)
-  ☐ Hurdle (+ cones)
-  ☐ Gaps (+ cones)
-  ☐ Chase ball (+ cones)

Real World Benchmarks: each with ``morning``, ``noon``, ``night``,
``depth``,

-  ☐ Curbs
-  ☐ Tables
-  ☐ Stairs
-  ☐ Ramps
-  ☐ Parkour

