**Skybox**: Each environment comes in lightings that corresponds to
different time of day.

-  ☐ daylight

-  ☐ dawn: yellow light, low incidence level (long shadow)

-  morning

-  evening: spotlight, low ambient, streetlight in the background

Setup
-----

Unfortunately, gym is a mess. You need the following versions

.. code-block:: shell

   pip install setuptools==65.5.0 pip==21 wheel==0.38.4
   pip install gym==0.21.0
   pip install gym-dmc==0.2.9
